full[is.na(full$KitchenQual),&quot;KitchenQual&quot;] &lt;- full$KitchenQual %&gt;% table %&gt;% sort %&gt;% names %&gt;% last %&gt;% as.numeric()
full$KitchenQual = as.integer(revalue(as.character(full$KitchenQual), Qualidade))
